name: Monster Cat
text: If this card is Special Summoned by the effect of "Stray Cat": Destroy as many Level 4 or lower monsters your opponent controls as possible, and if you do, inflict 400 damage to your opponent for each monster destroyed. Once per turn: You can target 1 "Stray Cat" or "Stray Cat Girl" in your Graveyard; add it to your hand.
